title: Live Composer v1.0.5.4 - Front-End WordPress Page Builder
description:
Live Composer is a front-end WordPress Page builder plugin. The front-end means you are building your posts and pages directly on the page, not in the admin.

Product page: http://codecanyon.net/item/live-composer-frontend-wordpress-page-builder/6594028

This plugin has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress plugin.
